OL,3,CShop staff 'facing Christmas crime
OL,4,Cwave' with more shoplifting cases
OL,5,Cunsolved
OL,7,FShop staff are facing a "Christmas
OL,8,Fcrime wave", an MP has warned as new
OL,9,Ffigures revealed an average of more
OL,10,Fthan 650 shoplifting offences a day
OL,11,Fwent unsolved in the past year.
OL,13,FIn the year to March 2024, 245,500
OL,14,Finvestigations were closed without a
OL,15,Fsuspect being identified ` an average
OL,16,Fof 672 a day ` according to analysis
OL,17,Ffrom the House of Commons Library.
