OL,5,Cunsolved
OL,7,FLiberal Democrat home affairs
OL,8,Fspokesperson Lisa Smart said: "Shop
OL,9,Fstaff are having to deal with a
OL,10,FChristmas crime wave as shoplifters
OL,11,Fact with impunity, with so many crimes
OL,12,Fbeing effectively legalised by the
OL,13,Fprevious Conservative government's
OL,14,Fshocking neglect.
OL,16,F"The new Government needs to get a
OL,17,Fgrip on this shoplifting epidemic, and
OL,18,Fhard-working shop staff on the
OL,19,Ffrontline need to be reassured that
OL,20,Fthey will not continue to be abandoned.
