OL,3,CShop staff 'facing Christmas crime
OL,4,Cwave' with more shoplifting cases
OL,5,Cunsolved
OL,7,F"That must start with ministers making
OL,8,Fsure that officers will actually have
OL,9,Fthe time and resources to focus on
OL,10,Ftheir local neighbourhoods and keep
OL,11,Fshop workers safe.
OL,13,F"Until that happens our communities
OL,14,Fwon't see the proper neighbourhood
OL,15,Fpolicing that they deserve."
OL,17,FThe data comes amid a rising level of
OL,18,Fshoplifting, with official figures
OL,19,Freleased in October showing the
OL,20,Foffence had hit a 20-year high.
