OL,7,FA total of 469,788 shoplifting
OL,8,Foffences were logged by forces in the
OL,9,Fyear to June 2024, up 29% on the
OL,10,F365,173 recorded in the previous 12
OL,11,Fmonths, and the highest annual figure
OL,12,Fsince current records began in the
OL,13,Fyear to March 2003.
OL,15,FIn November, the House of Lords
OL,16,FJustice and Home Affairs Committee
OL,17,Fwrote to policing minister Dame Diana
OL,18,FJohnson saying that shop theft is
OL,19,F"seriously underreported and not being
OL,20,Ftackled properly".
