OL,7,FIt said that the problem risks
OL,8,Fundermining confidence in the police
OL,9,Fand the criminal justice system.
OL,11,FA police squad set up to combat the
OL,12,Frise in shoplifting arrested 93
OL,13,Fmembers of organised crime gangs
OL,14,Fbehind retail theft within seven
OL,15,Fmonths, the National Police Chiefs'
OL,16,FCouncil announced earlier this month.
OL,18,FDame Diana said: "In the last year of
OL,19,Fthe Tory government, shoplifting
OL,20,Fsoared to a 20-year high, up 30% in
OL,21,Fjust 12 months.
